divs: Sighting DetailsAround, 12:30 a fast flying object going about 150 or more passed over my house heading east. It was triangular with two things sticking out of the front. It had weird writing on the bottom and looked to be flying backwards. It made a low humming sound. I had a friend with me he too saw it. It looked to be as big as 5 cars.
Summary: Fast flying grey object, triangle like
